text: I get a Quote: from this company and I was told that the inspection process I won't even know that I was here is what I was told. They were just taking some photographs. The guy shows up today from Travelers knocking on my door asking me about my dog asking me about the garage questions already spent a half an hour on the phone with the agent answering. In short I recommend you go local stay away from these internet sites. Thank God I never cancel my old policy!
